description: I’m not really sure how to describe these facemarks other than to say they look to me like they’re thinking. They’re all the same sort of style so here they are in a goup. It’s hard to know exactly how to name these thinking emoticons. You’ll see what I mean. בּ_בּ טּ_טּ לּ_לּ מּ_מּ סּ_סּ תּ_תּ
title: Some Kind of Style
